{"tid":2034562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：美突嚴查中國人！華駐美使館通告：多名公民離境遭長時間盤問 查手機電腦","createTime":"2020-05-25T09:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T12:24:44.000Z","uid":30743,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"44a431754fec6749fe85e9e0b7809b518d681edc","tid":2034562,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"自武漢肺炎肆虐全球，美國國土安全部早已進一步收緊入境政策，要求所有入境人士申報是否曾到中國。今日（25日），中國駐美國使館網站發出重要通知，提醒在美國的中國公民注意美國出境檢查，近日有多名中國公民反映，在出境時被美國海關長時間盤問，並檢查隨身攜帶的手機、電腦等電子設備，部份出境人士的電子設備更遭執法人員暫扣作進一步檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據美國法律，美國邊境海關執法人員有權對所有出入境者進行檢查，包括查驗其個人訊息、出入境目的，以及攜帶物品等等，無須事先申請搜查令。美國邊境執法人員毋須懷疑即可搜查旅客的手機等電子設備，並可對旅客電子設備進行升級搜查，或暫扣相關電子設備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國駐美國使館提醒，在美國的中國公民特別是留學生，注意美方出入境有關規定，提高自我保護意識，以免出境時對自己造成不便和損失。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐美國大使館網站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200525/NIAQIUPFZRZZL3QUJXI62XPTDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200525%2FNIAQIUPFZRZZL3QUJXI62XPTDE%2F&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3irXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=8b479741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200525%2FNIAQIUPFZRZZL3QUJXI62XPTDE%2F&h=679433bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200525/NIAQIUPFZRZZL3QUJXI62XPTDE/</a>"},{"pid":"a7155a0cd770a575ddf14257c30223709ccc7e38","tid":2034562,"uid":28159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac34a7bb25f28d97d4c9872bfef7f72fd161e771","tid":2034562,"uid":30743,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"日裔美國人囚禁（英文：Internment of Japanese Americans）是珍珠港事件發生以後，自1942年起，<span style=\"color: red;\">美國政府對約11萬居住在美國太平洋沿岸的日裔美國人的扣留，轉移和囚禁。</span>1942年2月19日，富蘭克林&middot;D&middot;羅斯福總統下達了9066號行政命令，授權美國陸軍部部長確定國內某些地區為「戰區」，並可以對生活在戰區的人加以任何必要的限制，甚至可以把他們排斥在戰區之外。這份命令聲明，整個太平洋沿岸，包括加利福尼亞州，俄勒岡州，華盛頓州和亞利桑那州的所有日裔美國人都可以被命令轉移。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%B0%8D%E6%97%A5%E8%A3%94%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9A%E7%A6%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25A3%2594%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259B%259A%25E7%25A6%2581&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3irXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=30421aa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%B0%8D%E6%97%A5%E8%A3%94%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9A%E7%A6%81</a><br />\n<br />\n歷史重温"},{"pid":"a6b4f9bebfce615816c508cc1c3f0a15fafecfa8","tid":2034562,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:58:40.000Z","msg":"唔干涉美國內政，拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc47cbd7999585fbbdd6ea2ee7d0263a1b2188b","tid":2034562,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"好有山雨欲來既feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850211eb6448ccbb51286c46e6e7611d62a185fb","tid":2034562,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"你得罪美帝，佢梗係封殺你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8423a8d149ab68cb4aa3f2f8bab255ceda2ad130","tid":2034562,"uid":55568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac34a7bb25f28d97d4c9872bfef7f72fd161e771","tid":2034562,"uid":30743,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T09:57:30.000Z","msg":"日裔美國人囚禁（英文：Internment of Japanese Americans）是珍珠港事件發生以後，自1942年起，<span style=\"color: red;\">美國政府對約11萬居住在美國太平洋沿岸的日裔美國人的扣留，轉移和囚禁。</span>1942年2月19日，富蘭克林&middot;D&middot;羅斯福總統下達了9066號行政命令，授權美國陸軍部部長確定國內某些地區為「戰區」，並可以對生活在戰區的人加以任何必要的限制，甚至可以把他們排斥在戰區之外。這份命令聲明，整個太平洋沿岸，包括加利福尼亞州，俄勒岡州，華盛頓州和亞利桑那州的所有日裔美國人都可以被命令轉移。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%B0%8D%E6%97%A5%E8%A3%94%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9A%E7%A6%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25A3%2594%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259B%259A%25E7%25A6%2581&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3irXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=30421aa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%B0%8D%E6%97%A5%E8%A3%94%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9A%E7%A6%81</a><br />\n<br />\n歷史重温"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"然後就出現最強日裔部隊"},{"pid":"9f37f4022646065b5409399f24b1ac7c27f208e9","tid":2034562,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:57:27.000Z","msg":"呢班支那人可能係中共的間諜"},{"pid":"61862212412dcff87c5b9103209626a3fc4cc6ed","tid":2034562,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"亮劍！"}]}